name: Degen Arena
description: Degen Arena is the first free play to earn game on PC and mobile featuring your favorite meme coin characters. Jump into the action. Crazy fights wild energy and nonstop fun. Only one can come out on top. Welcome to the Arena, degens. Climb fast or fall hard. Endless tower, rising fog, and players trying to push you off. Stay alive, stay on top. Team battle for the bag. Grab the cash, hold it longer than the other team, and don't get jacked.
